Rewrite the entire following OpenAPI 3.1.0 specification, incorporating the necessary corrections to ensure the label-related actions (specifically under the `/labels` and `/labels/{label_id}` paths) appear as testable actions and function correctly with a GPT. Ensure the rewritten specification matches the exact formatting and structure of the original, including indentation, comments, and the order of elements. Only correct syntax errors and structural problems within the existing label action definitions. Do not add any new paths or operations that are not already present in the original specification. The corrected specification must be a valid OpenAPI 3.1.0 document.

Here is the original OpenAPI specification:

```yaml
openapi: 3.1.0
info:
  title: Todoist REST API
  description: |-
    This is the official documentation for the Todoist REST API v2, focusing on core resources: Projects,
      Sections, Tasks, Comments, and Labels.
  version: 2.0.0
servers:
  - url: https://api.todoist.com/rest/v2
    description: Main (production) server
components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT
      description: Use your personal API token in the format 'Bearer {token}' to authenticate requests.
  schemas:
    Project:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          description: Project ID.
        name:
          type: string
          description: Project name.
        color:
          type: string
          description: The color of the project icon. Refer to the name column in the Colors guide for more info.
        parent_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: ID of parent project (will be null for top-level projects).
        order:
          type: integer
          description: Project position under the same parent (read-only).
        comment_count:
          type: integer
          description: Number of project comments.
        is_shared:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the project is shared (read-only).
        is_favorite:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the project is a favorite.
        is_inbox_project:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the project is the user's Inbox (read-only).
        is_team_inbox:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the project is the Team Inbox (read-only).
        view_style:
          type: string
          enum:
            - list
            - board
          description: Determines the way the project is displayed within the Todoist clients.
        url:
          type: string
          description: URL to access this project in the Todoist web or mobile applications.
      required:
        - id
        - name
    ProjectCreate:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          description: Name of the project (required).
        parent_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Parent project ID.
        color:
          type: string
          description: The color of the project icon.
        is_favorite:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the project is a favorite.
        view_style:
          type: string
          enum:
            - list
            - board
          description: The view style for the project.
      required:
        - name
    ProjectUpdate:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          description: New name of the project.
        color:
          type: string
          description: The color of the project icon.
        is_favorite:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the project is a favorite.
        view_style:
          type: string
          enum:
            - list
            - board
          description: The view style for the project.
    Section:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          description: Section ID.
        project_id:
          type: string
          description: Project ID to which the section belongs.
        order:
          type: integer
          description: Position of the section among others in the same project.
        name:
          type: string
          description: Section name.
      required:
        - id
        - project_id
        - name
    SectionCreate:
      type: object
      properties:
        project_id:
          type: string
          description: The project ID this section belongs to (required).
        name:
          type: string
          description: Name of the section (required).
        order:
          type: integer
          description: Optional position among sections.
      required:
        - project_id
        - name
    SectionUpdate:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          description: New name of the section.
    Task:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          description: Task ID.
        project_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Task’s project ID (read-only).
        section_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: ID of the section this task belongs to (null if none).
        content:
          type: string
          description: Task content.
        description:
          type: string
          description: A description for the task.
        is_completed:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the task is completed.
        labels:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          description: A list of label names.
        priority:
          type: integer
          description: Task priority from 1 (normal) to 4 (urgent).
        order:
          type: integer
          description: Non-zero integer used by clients to sort tasks.
        due:
          type: object
          nullable: true
          description: An object representing the task's due date/time.
        url:
          type: string
          description: URL to access this task in the Todoist web or mobile apps (read-only).
      required:
        - id
        - content
        - is_completed
    TaskCreate:
      type: object
      properties:
        content:
          type: string
          description: Task content (required).
        description:
          type: string
          description: Optional description for the task.
        project_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: The project ID for the new task.
        section_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: The section ID for the new task.
        parent_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: ID of the parent task.
        order:
          type: integer
          description: Sort position of the task in the project or section.
        labels:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          description: A list of label names.
        priority:
          type: integer
          description: Task priority from 1 (normal) to 4 (urgent).
        due_string:
          type: string
          description: Human-defined due date.
        due_date:
          type: string
          format: date
          description: Specific due date in YYYY-MM-DD.
        due_datetime:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          description: Specific date and time in RFC3339 format in UTC.
        due_lang:
          type: string
          description: 2-letter code for language (if due_string is not in English).
        assignee_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: The responsible user ID for a shared task.
        duration:
          type: integer
          nullable: true
          description: A positive integer for the amount of time (in duration_unit).
        duration_unit:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Unit of time for duration, must be 'minute' or 'day'.
      required:
        - content
    TaskUpdate:
      type: object
      properties:
        content:
          type: string
          description: New content for the task.
        description:
          type: string
          description: New description for the task.
        labels:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          description: Updated list of label names.
        priority:
          type: integer
          description: Updated task priority.
        due_string:
          type: string
          description: Updated human-defined due date.
        due_date:
          type: string
          format: date
          description: Updated date in YYYY-MM-DD.
        due_datetime:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          description: Updated date and time in RFC3339 format in UTC.
        due_lang:
          type: string
          description: 2-letter code specifying language for due_string.
        assignee_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Updated responsible user ID or null to unset.
        duration:
          type: integer
          nullable: true
          description: A positive integer for the amount of time the task requires, or null to unset.
        duration_unit:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Must be 'minute' or 'day' if duration is specified, or null to unset.
    Comment:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          description: Comment ID.
        task_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: The comment's task ID (null if belongs to project).
        project_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: The comment's project ID (null if belongs to task).
        posted_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          description: Date/time when comment was added (UTC, RFC3339).
        content:
          type: string
          description: Comment content (may contain markdown).
        attachment:
          type: object
          nullable: true
          description: Optional attachment object (null if none).
      required:
        - id
        - content
    CommentCreate:
      type: object
      properties:
        task_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: The task ID this comment belongs to (required if project_id not set).
        project_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: The project ID this comment belongs to (required if task_id not set).
        content:
          type: string
          description: Comment text (required).
        attachment:
          type: object
          nullable: true
          description: Optional attachment object.
      required:
        - content
    CommentUpdate:
      type: object
      properties:
        content:
          type: string
          description: Updated comment text (may contain markdown).
    Label:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          description: Label ID.
        name:
          type: string
          description: Label name.
        color:
          type: string
          description: The color of the label icon.
        order:
          type: integer
          description: Number used by clients to sort list of labels.
        is_favorite:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the label is a favorite.
      required:
        - id
        - name
    LabelCreate:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          description: Name of the label (required).
        order:
          type: integer
          description: Label order.
        color:
          type: string
          description: The color of the label icon.
        is_favorite:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the label is a favorite.
      required:
        - name
    LabelUpdate:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          description: New name for the label.
        order:
          type: integer
          description: New label order.
        color:
          type: string
          description: New color of the label icon.
        is_favorite:
          type: boolean
          description: Whether the label is a favorite.
    LabelSharedRename:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          description: Existing shared label name.
        new_name:
          type: string
          description: New name for the shared label.
      required:
        - name
        - new_name
    LabelSharedRemove:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          description: The name of the shared label to remove.
      required:
        - name
    Error:
      type: object
      properties:
        error:
          type: string
          description: Error message.
